1
00:00:03,937 --> 00:00:07,374
There's no chance you'd get into
any college with your standard score.

2
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:08,508
Don't say that.

3
00:00:08,575 --> 00:00:10,877
I want to go to the same place
as Naomi Kawashima.

4
00:00:10,944 --> 00:00:12,278
You mean AGU?

5
00:00:12,345 --> 00:00:15,115
You wouldn't even make it
into their kindergarten, silly!

6
00:00:15,181 --> 00:00:16,316
If I don't go to college,

7
00:00:16,383 --> 00:00:19,519
I can't become Miss Campus
or appear on <i>All Night Fuji</i>.

8
00:00:19,586 --> 00:00:22,555
I'll take the back door route
to Ferris if I have to.

9
00:00:23,390 --> 00:00:25,291
You're her mother. Tell her.

10
00:00:25,358 --> 00:00:26,960
I'm not her mother.

11
00:00:27,560 --> 00:00:29,396
I thought you married her father.

12
00:00:29,462 --> 00:00:31,264
Absolutely not. That's not even funny--

13
00:00:31,331 --> 00:00:32,198
Father.

14
00:00:32,265 --> 00:00:34,467
No. You're not getting it, do you?

15
00:00:35,035 --> 00:00:36,569
You're the father.

16
00:00:37,337 --> 00:00:38,171
Yes.

17
00:00:39,472 --> 00:00:40,874
But you're my father.

18
00:00:42,509 --> 00:00:46,179
Your daughter wanted me
to talk to her father, so here I am.

19
00:00:47,680 --> 00:00:50,016
I mean, sure, I'm a father too.

20
00:00:50,083 --> 00:00:51,384
I've got a daughter as well.

21
00:00:53,420 --> 00:00:55,321
-Father.
-Weren't you listening?

22
00:00:55,388 --> 00:00:58,458
Call me father one more time,
and who knows what might happen!

23
00:00:59,025 --> 00:01:00,293
I sent you something.

24
00:01:00,860 --> 00:01:01,694
Huh?

25
00:01:02,362 --> 00:01:04,531
Listen, Ogawa, with your looks,

26
00:01:04,597 --> 00:01:06,900
